There's an `@Mock` annotation you can use that works with generics:
```suggestion
  @Mock
  private GossipedOperationConsumer<ValidateableAttestation> gossipedAttestationConsumer;
```

If you go with this, you need to annotate the test class with `@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)` I think.

