timeline.body:
I think you could simplify this by keeping `maxNumberOfElements` as an instance var:
```suggestion
  public OperationPool(Class<T> clazz, OperationStateTransitionValidator<T> operationValidator) {
    this.operationValidator = operationValidator;
    this.maxNumberOfElements = maxNumberOfElementsInBlock.get(clazz);
  }
```

Or even cutting out `clazz` altogether:
```suggestion
  public OperationPool(OperationStateTransitionValidator<T> operationValidator, final int maxElements) {
    this.operationValidator = operationValidator;
    this.maxNumberOfElements = maxElements;
  }
```

